headline: Why Pfizer (PFE) Stock Is Trading Up Today
summary: Shares of global pharmaceutical company Pfizer (NYSE:PFE) jumped 5.9% in the afternoon session after the company reached an agreement with the U.S. government to lower drug prices and reported positive trial data for a weight-loss drug from a recently acquired company.
